                            <comment id="16638026" author="sebb@apache.org" created="Thu, 4 Oct 2018 10:06:01 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Also the host dist.apache.org is not intended for public use.&lt;br/&gt;
It is only intended for use in pushing the release to the ASF mirror system.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;KEYS, sigs and hashes must use links to&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.apache.org/dist/beam/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://www.apache.org/dist/beam/&lt;/a&gt;...&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The source artifact must be linked using the ASF mirror system, e.g.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.apache.org/dyn/closer.lua/beam/2.7.0/apache-beam-2.7.0-source-release.zip&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://www.apache.org/dyn/closer.lua/beam/2.7.0/apache-beam-2.7.0-source-release.zip&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17131746" author="beamjirabot" created="Wed, 10 Jun 2020 17:25:38 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This issue is P2 but has been unassigned without any comment for 60 days so it has been labeled &quot;stale-P2&quot;. If this issue is still affecting you, we care! Please comment and remove the label. Otherwise, in 14 days the issue will be moved to P3.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Please see &lt;a href=&quot;https://beam.apache.org/contribute/jira-priorities/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://beam.apache.org/contribute/jira-priorities/&lt;/a&gt; for a detailed explanation of what these priorities mean.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
